```

Delivery Managers LOVE structured answers.

---

### 3ï¸âƒ£ Use DM to protect QA time

If testing is squeezed:

> â€œIf testing time is reduced by 1 day, regression coverage drops by ~30%. Risk of production defects increases.â€

